    "title": "[Diffusion] Fix weight scale swizzle and add large-M kernel config for FLUX.2-dev-NVFP4",
    "user": {
      "login": "RubiaCx",
      "id": 78632976,
      "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjc4NjMyOTc2",
