    "body": "## Motivation\r\n\r\nTwo bugs in the diffusion FLUX.2-dev-NVFP4 path:\r\n\r\n1. `ModelOptFp4LinearMethod.process_weights_after_loading()` was missing the blockwise interleave (swizzle) required by CUTLASS TMA kernels. The CUTLASS fallback path silently produced wrong results, caused ~5% cosine-similarity drop vs cuDNN.\r\n2. `KernelConfigDefault` (cluster `4×4`) left ~25% of the last M-wave idle for FLUX.2 at 1024px (M≈4352, N=3072).\r\n\r\nAlso removes the `comfy-kitchen` third-party dependency.\r\n\r\n## Modifications\r\n\r\n- **`nvfp4_scaled_mm_kernels.cuh`**: Add `KernelConfigLargeM` (cluster `1×4`) for M > 1024; narrow `KernelConfigDefault` to M ∈ (256, 1024] with cluster `2×4`.\r\n- **`modelopt_quant.py`**: Add missing `reshape + permute` swizzle in `process_weights_after_loading`; remove `ComfyUIFp4LinearMethod` and `_get_comfy_kitchen_cuda_backend`.\r\n- **`cuda.py`**: Remove comfy-kitchen platform detection methods.\r\n\r\n## Speed Tests and Profiling\r\n\r\nNo regression. Denoise 50 steps on FLUX.2-dev-NVFP4 on B200:\r\n- cuDNN: ~0.326 s/step\r\n- CUTLASS: ~0.292 s/step\r\n\r\n## Checklist\r\n\r\n- [x] Format your code according to the [Format code with pre-commit](https://docs.sglang.io/developer_guide/contribution_guide.html#format-code-with-pre-commit).\r\n- [ ] Add unit tests according to the [Run and add unit tests](https://docs.sglang.io/developer_guide/contribution_guide.html#run-and-add-unit-tests).\r\n- [ ] Update documentation according to [Write documentations](https://docs.sglang.io/developer_guide/contribution_guide.html#write-documentations).\r\n- [x] Provide accuracy and speed benchmark results according to [Test the accuracy](https://docs.sglang.io/developer_guide/contribution_guide.html#test-the-accuracy) and [Benchmark the speed](https://docs.sglang.io/developer_guide/contribution_guide.html#benchmark-the-speed).\r\n- [ ] Follow the SGLang code style [guidance](https://docs.sglang.io/developer_guide/contribution_guide.html#code-style-guidance).",
